37 void getRPYFromQuaternionMSG(geometry_msgs::Quaternion orientation, double& roll,double& pitch, double& yaw)
38 {
39  tf::Quaternion quat;
40  tf::quaternionMsgToTF(orientation,quat);
41  quat.normalize();
42  tf::Matrix3x3 mat(quat);
43  mat.getRPY(roll, pitch,yaw);
44 }
